===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Elio (Masters)}}
Elio, in his {{g|Sun and Moon}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Popplio}} and its evolved forms {{p|Brionne}} and {{p|Primarina}}, along with {{p|Espeon}}, {{p|Stakataka}}, {{Shiny}} {{form|Necrozma|Dusk Mane}} {{p|Necrozma}}, and {{p|Decidueye}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Elio became a playable sync pair on April 17, 2021.

Elio first appeared as an NPC during the [[story event]] [[Trials on the Isle]]. He has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. Unlike in the original games, both Elio and {{mas|Selene}} coexist in this game.

